Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.21,0:01:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.52,0:02:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He won, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please arrange a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.53,0:02:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.16,0:02:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like usual you.{no clue what else 普通ならね means here}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.83,0:02:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so into him.\NI'm jealous of this kid, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He will eventually become
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.47,0:02:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,dozens times stronger than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:39.11,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fade(700,700)\an8\c&HFBFDFE&\bord0\shad2\blur0.5\4c&H696256&\b1\fnHitch Hike\fs45\4a&H00&}Episode 14\N {\fs92}Backbone{lit is "human back" but that is A) too bulky B) doesn't make more sense than backbone}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.84,0:02:49.81,Song,,0,0,0,,Bronze{/Copper}-Silk Dream{can only be a proper name, no other way around, maybe "Rome" or "roman dream" - 銅羅夢}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:51.78,Song,,0,0,0,,To Mr. Shibaura Futoshi \NTokyo, Nakano Ward, Fujigasa 110{I made up this part, there's no such city, but I can't figure this 藤ヶ佐 thing, and can't be arsed - it doesn't matter anyhow}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left now is to refurnish the hardware{/the appearance}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yozakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.12,0:03:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The name for this series{/generation/machine}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He used to cherish you once.{Lit is "I had a crush on you" but I have no clue who he refers to - I would like to hope it's the machine, but it's still a heluva weird thing to say and sounds very awkward in combination with next two lines; taken those next lines into account, it all points towards Kojiro that he had a crush on, but that's even more out of place and out of blue shounen-ai sequence and I don't remember them coming out as gays later on}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,As a man too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still resent{/hold a grudge on} me, Kojiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.10,0:03:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A'morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it going, how's it going? \NWhy so sullen a face?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, it's a love letter, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk nonsense. Just a note from a friend. \NAn old-time one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.72,0:03:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you sleep well last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:03:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure did! \NLike a log!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.39,0:04:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of, thanks for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a treat from Doctor{/on Doctor's expense}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He was mighty happy, \Nwith your promotion to Knight and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.07,0:04:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi, I wonder how he is doing.{/if he is okay.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He sure was thoroughly boozed yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:18.25,Song,,0,0,0,,To Mr. Shibaura Futoshi \NTokyo, Nakano Ward, Fujigasa 110
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.19,0:04:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It arrived yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a letter from your pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:40.29,Song,,0,0,0,,To Mr. Shibaura Futoshi \NTokyo, Nakano Ward, Fujigasa 110
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.92,0:04:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Master is not as easy one \Nto catch red-handed after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you occasionally receive a love letter, \Nit's no big deal showing it to others.{unsure, it may mean "But if you receive a love letter, it's not something you show others" but it contradicts previous lines}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya, you'll have to figure on your own \Nwhat to think of Kojiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But let me tell you just this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In what I said, there was no lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to our place!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.95,0:05:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess, you must still be mad at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.59,0:05:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I still am.{Lit would be "-Surely, you're still at me... -...Mad.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.83,0:05:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But with so few regular customers, \Nwe can't really afford to alienate{/treating with enmity} any.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Because treating them with a smile \Nis good for business.{/So I just put up a customer service smile.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you up to?{Lit: What do we do about it? Like usual is okay. - this is utterly cryptic and senseless to me} \NThe usual thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.34,0:05:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear customer, did something stick to my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But say...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.72,0:06:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You made up your mind to treat me to dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, today I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Yuri. \NOn the 23rd, I'll be away{ from home}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really important.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it? Well, can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But once I'm back, \NI'll treat you to dinner at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me where you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{Going }To settle one old score{/dispute}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Settle the score, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this pretentious wording?{/Are you trying to look cool this way?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Young Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.57,0:06:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Gen?{I hope it is Gen and not anything else}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:07:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Not feeling well?{/You got sick?}\NYour face is so pale{/blue}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a hangover.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a no-way to go! \NYou have to take a better care of your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it there, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.94,0:07:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did Daiba come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you let this kid meet his father?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the matter he should decide himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.19,0:08:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When you meet him, what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:04.09,Song,,0,0,0,,Nagasawa
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.93,0:08:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You like this fellow, Ginya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,As for me, I like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I can't know \Nwhat becomes of this guy later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason, I have faith on Ginya's account.{/in Ginya.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:48.54,Song,,0,0,0,,Nagasawa Station
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I was a bit too naive{/rash}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it won't be that easy to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:50.51,Song,,0,0,0,,Shinba—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.74,0:08:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.51,0:08:52.38,Song,,0,0,0,,Shinbashi Koketsu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:09:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, look. \NThere's someone using payphone{/public phone} in this age!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he lose his cellphone or what?{Lit: I wonder if he doesn't have a cellphone.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Still looks rather young, in his 30s.{I could only hear "Still young" so the rest is a guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?{guess} Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Fools! It's not about a cellphone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You happen to know the guy on this picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this some perverted kind of pickup?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,His fly is open!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm out of ideas.{guess; he says "I'm exhausted\tired" but I can only see it as "I exhausted the ways"}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What did that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.74,0:09:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It was too rash to come unprepared after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let me do it just for a short minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:09:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But we'll be in trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.85,0:10:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about that. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.26,0:10:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if someone comes in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. \NWe'll be done in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Doctor! I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.19,0:10:14.66,Song,,0,0,0,,{Dangerous }{this word is not really meaningful, but omitting it reliefs the cps greatly}\NNo running in the hallway!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Shunichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to tell me about a patient \Nby the name of Daiba Ryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Medical chart?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.24,0:10:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Had to do a bit of cajolery to extract it.{/Finding it was a bit troublesome.}
Comment: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:35.86,Song,,0,0,0,,Nagasawa Parlor \NVacant machines{parlor is in eigo so there's no need to translate the rest}{couln'd really figure out that machines part, it reads "free car" or "taxi available for hiring" but how tf this relates to a pachislot parlor}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't think I can help you...{/I don't know.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This photo is from 17 years ago, \Nso he probably looks rather like a grandpa now, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing is not serial.{/There's no such thing.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I have never seen it. When it comes to pachislot, \NI'm quite a connoisseur, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.47,0:10:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, this one \Nnever made it to production.{/was never released for an open market.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from early generations, right? \NMust be Unit 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:11:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt so great to press buttons on those{/play at}{guess}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll ask people around{/look into it.} \Nabout this machine{/generation}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,0:11:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no. It's not about the machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you tried asking \Nin the police box across the street?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,About this person. If he lives around here, \Nthey must know something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.66,0:11:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No alms for runaways.{/Run away from your home, did you?/I'm not an almsgiver.}{I'm not sure about any of the words here: it may be both a "runaway from home child" and "almsgiver" but not those two together}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I'm looking for a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.27,0:11:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you yesterday around 3 PM?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.13,0:11:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday? Lemme...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In Nagasawa, in front of the Station, I think{/around that}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We received a report, \Nthe perpetrator features{/stature/height} are just like yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:11:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A molester.{/pervert/hentai}{xDD}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.98,0:12:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.77,0:12:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Under the pretext of showing some photo, \Nhe approaches high school girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then all of a sudden drops his pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it there! \NI never dropped my pants or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They all say so.{/Yeah, I figured.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what the hell did I got myself into?{/In the middle of what did I suddenly found myself!?}{everything past "What" is a guesswork, I have no clue for the real meaning behind 何中に出かけてんですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,In the hypophysis, \Nthere is a{ relatively big} malign tumor of significant size.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a detailed checkup, \NI can't tell more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.34,0:12:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The danger{/risk} is significant as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Shunichi, what is your exact relation to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman accompanying him \Nalso asked his case to be kept in a low profile.{Lit: Received an order to keep quiet from the woman that chaperoned him. - it's still unclear to me whether she shut up Daiba or doctors}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This morning, he sneaked out of hospital \Nwithout permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sneaked out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what kind of man is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He manages to keep going quite well \Neven in that condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You feeling better?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Today it's such a nice weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll go out to do some shopping. \NYou want to eat something specific?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.27,0:13:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Your real father then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,However, we don't have anyone \Nnamed Shinbashi Kojiro in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.60,0:13:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.10,0:13:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unfortunate.{/Is that so?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.24,0:13:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure I've heard it somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.04,0:13:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, yes. \NThe fraternity{/Yūai-en - they don't really act like a usual fraternity organization would so maybe keeping a native name would make sense, or maybe just double down and go for some pension/kindegarden/park of friendship and love} in the neighboring city.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraternity?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Daiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Today's matches have not yet started...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.81,0:14:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My seat is not taken, is it?{guess, this is hardest one yet, no fucking clue what seat this is about, maybe like parking lot or in a car or his position like King or his spectator's seat which I decided upon eventually, nor do I even know if this is a question or a request, though it has to be one of those for the guard to answer "yes"}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.15,0:14:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Kojiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.61,0:14:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You learned to fold it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how it goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, no way it ever goes this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.71,0:14:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{Fraternity}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you sent here for anything?{goyou is some official business/errand but I don't see how to incorporate that and I guess it has to do with the Fraternity activity}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You need help with some matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing of the kind. \NSorry I interrupted you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.94,0:15:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.82,0:16:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.17,0:16:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraternity?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You shitting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.54,0:16:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He let mom die alone!{guess, he says just "mom is dead [y'know]" but I don't see etc}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.09,0:16:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.72,0:16:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom's name...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,At that moment, dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.31,0:16:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't! You shouldn't let him{/this man} in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad came to the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you come in and let mom see you?{/to meet mom?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,With your own actions, \Nyou brought such deep wounds upon everyone{/cornered yourself into causing...}!{/You put yourself in a position to cause such deep wounds.}{guess - as always, it's unclear whose wounds he refers to as well as whose actions let to it, maybe he even blames uncle or himself for not ushering pops in; the part in the beginning is hard to discern, maybe something like "from me very childhood" hides in it as it would fit the context perfectly + I never figured that "sei" part}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.25,0:17:56.22,Song,,0,0,0,,Fraternity
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now. \NEveryone, gather up for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.61,0:18:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, head inside and wash your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's battle between Knights \Nwill start at the prescheduled time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.29,0:19:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You act just like those previous weaklings{guess, I never figured "okanetsura" part}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can smell at once \Nwhenever I'm dealing with the small fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But speaking frankly, today, \NI totally don't feel like losing to the kinds of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, we are proceeding \Nto begin the battle between Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Game starts in 10 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,5 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,3...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,2...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,1...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Game start!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.55,0:20:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:20:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Before long, I will knock your door!{/Soon already, I will reach your place!}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.29,0:22:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.15,0:22:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Full name.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.54,0:22:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.75,0:22:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Obstinacy.{guess}{I feel the word here has something to do with medicine but I don't care}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.06,0:22:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.98,0:22:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.07,0:22:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{[Medical] }Chart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.69,0:22:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My finger will stop the time.
